In [109]:
idx_l = []
words_l = []
for each in df.index:
    if each in stop_words:
        idx_l.append(each)
    words_l.append(nltk.PorterStemmer().stem(str(each)))
        
df = df.drop(idx_l, axis=0)

LDA for topic clustering¶

In [145]:
from sklearn.decomposition import NMF, LatentDirichletAllocation
from time import time

lda = LatentDirichletAllocation(
    n_components=10,
    max_iter=10,
    learning_method="online",
    learning_offset=50.0,
    random_state=0,
)
t0 = time()
lda.fit(preprocessed_df.transpose())
print("done in %0.3fs." % (time() - t0))

done in 57.097s.
In [282]:
n_top_words = 20
feature_names = preprocessed_df.index.values

fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 5, figsize=(30, 15), sharex=True)
axes = axes.flatten()
for topic_idx, topic in enumerate(lda.components_):
    top_features_ind = topic.argsort()[: -n_top_words - 1 : -1]
    top_features = [feature_names[i] for i in top_features_ind]
    weights = topic[top_features_ind]

    ax = axes[topic_idx]
    ax.barh(top_features, weights, height=0.7)
    ax.set_title(f"Topic {topic_idx +1}", fontdict={"fontsize": 30})
    ax.invert_yaxis()
    ax.tick_params(axis="both", which="major", labelsize=20)
    for i in "top right left".split():
        ax.spines[i].set_visible(False)
    fig.suptitle("Words' Topics in LDA", fontsize=40)

plt.subplots_adjust(top=0.90, bottom=0.05, wspace=0.90, hspace=0.3)
plt.show()

k means¶

In [174]:
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn import metrics
In [243]:
ch_score = []
ss_score = []
inertia = []
for k in range(2,25):
    clf = KMeans(n_clusters=k,max_iter=1000, init="k-means++")
    pred = clf.fit_predict(topics_df)
    ch = metrics.calinski_harabasz_score(topics_df,pred)
    ss = metrics.silhouette_score(topics_df,pred)
    ch_score.append(ch)
    ss_score.append(ss)
    inertia.append(clf.inertia_)

manifold¶

In [207]:
from sklearn import manifold
In [240]:
n_neighbors = 18  # neighborhood which is used to recover the locally linear structure
n_components = 2  # number of coordinates for the manifold

params = {
    "n_neighbors": n_neighbors,
    "n_components": n_components,
    "eigen_solver": "dense",
    "random_state": 0,
}

lle_standard = manifold.LocallyLinearEmbedding(method="standard", **params)
X_standard = lle_standard.fit_transform(topics_df)

#lle_ltsa = manifold.LocallyLinearEmbedding(method="ltsa", **params)
#X_ltsa = lle_ltsa.fit_transform(topics_df)

#lle_hessian = manifold.LocallyLinearEmbedding(method="hessian", **params)
#X_hessian = lle_hessian.fit_transform(topics_df)

lle_mod = manifold.LocallyLinearEmbedding(method="modified", **params)
X_mod = lle_mod.fit_transform(topics_df)
